These are Puzzles for 7x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-1-1::.
2 different games are played: scrabble, mah-jongg
There are 2 different favourite colors: light-blue, ebony
There 2 different types of food: raspberry, apricot
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: punk, ambient
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: chaman, siglo
House: tower, palace
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: skateboarding, lacrosse
1. the person playing scrabble is on the far right##1
2. the person eating apricot is on the far right##1
3. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the person who likes ebony##1
4. the tower house is the siglo-smoker##1
5. the fan of ambient is on the far left##1
6. the palace house is on the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |
| Game      | mah-jongg     | scrabble       |
| Color         | light-blue   | ebony     |
| Food           | raspberry | apricot   |
| Music-Genre   | ambient   | punk  |
| Cigar   | siglo | chaman |
| House           | tower      | palace     |
| Sport     | lacrosse    | skateboarding   |

