.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-1-2::.
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: parkour, rugby
There 2 different types of food: cucumber, onion
There are 2 different favourite colors: orange, green
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: rose, begonia
2 different games are played: chess, backgammon
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: dannemann, chaman
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: romance, animation
1. the person who likes green is on the right of the person eating onion##1
2. the chaman-smoker is the person watching animation movies##1
3. the person watching romance movies is on the left of the person who growsrose##1
4. the person playing backgammon is on the far right##1
5. the person who's sport is parkour is the dannemann-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |
| Sport      | parkour    | rugby |
| Food         | onion        | cucumber  |
| Color           | orange | green  |
| Flower   | begonia            | rose    |
| Game   | chess     | backgammon   |
| Cigar           | dannemann         | chaman    |
| Movie-Genre     | romance           | animation      |

